        "action": "Introduce a legal minimum and maximum working temperature for bus driver cabs.",
        "additional_details": "",
        "background": "Driver cabs in buses are often 5 degrees extra than external temperature. Currently drivers are driving in 38 degree cabs with no air con and no cold air, just warm air blowing into a glass and plastic cab. It is incredibly hard to concentrate on safe driving in these conditions.",
